    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to the culture of one of the three main divisions of the Sioux. The Yankton is comprised of the Yankton and Yanktonai.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
